race.description: Vamoose At Sires On Ice Division1
race.comment: APPENZELL (3) has been in sparkling form, last time overcoming a chequered run to win a Other at this track (19.41) and making it three straight wins. Tough to beat again. SEATON (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 14 times for nine wins and three minors. Placed last time (26.16) at this track in a Grade 4, finishing second and beaten 1.3 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SIMPLY DANGER (8) is a promising dog in the frame at 26 of 56 starts including 12 wins and was in the minors again latest (30.24) over 515m at Launceston. Has a good record here at this journey. Expected to feature on best form. CAL'S SENSATION (2) generally performs well from this box.
